I don't know why, but somehow this is one of my favorite series out of the entire website. For those wanting to start, here are some disclaimers:
1) Chronological order follows as so : 234932  235529  247540  262543  326882
2) It's already obvious from the tags, but its an NTR story, so don't get your hopes too high or expect a feel good ending - cuz it won't happen
3) If you don't like the feeling of seeing the boyfriend getting cucked, try imagining this as revenge NTR, with the sensei being the main protagonist getting back at an ungrateful student who shows no respect whatsoever. You'd still feel like trash at the end but at least it won't be too depressing, at least that was how I felt going in.
4) If you still end up hating on this story, then thats ok as well, tt's your opinion. But don't start hating on other people just cuz they have different fetishes or tastes than you. ( I ain't a fan of NTR, this story might as well be the only exception)
